1.To add connection- nmcli con add type ethernet con-name hello ifname ens33 192.168.0.96/24 gw4 192.168.0.98 

2.To check configurations-  cat ifcfg-hello

3.To activate connection-  nmcli connection up <con-name>

4  To view all connection-  nmcli connection show

5   To delete connection-  nmcli connection delete <con-name>

6   To reload connection-   nmcli connection reload

7   To view specific connection-  nmcli connection show <co-name>

8   To down the connection-  nmcli con down <static>

9   To see general status-  nmcli general status
